Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.00,0:00:12.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翻译：taku
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.58,0:00:09.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,韩语讲座第四回
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.16,0:00:11.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{300,0}大家好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.23,0:00:14.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{300,0}我是你们的老师佐野茜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.27,0:00:16.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{300,0}大家好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.36,0:00:18.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{300,0}我是伊吹庆太
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.32,0:00:20.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{300,0}大家好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.73,0:00:22.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{300,0}我是小黑
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.51,0:00:27.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请大家好好跟着我们一起进行学习
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.38,0:00:30.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天第四回了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.67,0:00:35.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们来试着学习韩语中的[可以...吗？]句型
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.00,0:00:36.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.71,0:00:37.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.75,0:00:41.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么和之前一样先从我开始
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.94,0:00:48.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小茜  这里人山人海啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.36,0:00:51.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千万不能走散了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.32,0:00:56.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小茜  牵紧我的手迈小步走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.26,0:00:59.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,庆太~
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.96,0:01:08.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以牵手吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.78,0:01:19.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小茜又在发呆了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.95,0:01:22.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃...啊啊  来回顾一下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.01,0:01:29.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,[...hedo derukayo？（韩语）]就是日语中[可以...吗？]的句型
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.57,0:01:30.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很简单吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.52,0:01:33.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们两个好好想一想场景
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.72,0:01:35.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先从庆太开始
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.53,0:01:36.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.37,0:01:37.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.35,0:01:51.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(可以在这坐下吗)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.17,0:01:58.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好~  做的非常不错
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.87,0:02:03.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,庆太的话  我可以开车送你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.77,0:02:06.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？ 小茜你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.79,0:02:07.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.52,0:02:09.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.78,0:02:11.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么接下来是小黑
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.36,0:02:13.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  我会加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.60,0:02:32.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(可以再去另一家店吃饭吗)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.09,0:02:39.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一家店不够你吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.51,0:02:42.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是...可是...人家就想多吃一点嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.09,0:02:46.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来  你的韩语讲的真棒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.61,0:02:47.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.07,0:02:50.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每晚睡觉前我都有好好学习哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.93,0:02:53.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小茜  你说我韩语讲的怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.30,0:02:56.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊...确实讲的很流畅哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.95,0:02:59.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小黑  下回教教我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.18,0:03:00.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.68,0:03:03.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,庆太  今晚就开始进行特训吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.79,0:03:05.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚开始我一定要加油了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.02,0:03:07.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么先来决定晚餐吃什么吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.94,0:03:08.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.45,0:03:09.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大酱汤  石锅拌饭....(所举均为韩国料理)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.97,0:03:11.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么啊  庆太
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.91,0:03:16.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好看着我的话随时都可以给你特训
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.69,0:03:23.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以哭吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.18,0:03:25.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,


